body.description: Say goodbye to overnight leakage with new and improved Pampers Swaddlers Overnights. Our best diapers for overnight now feature a Blowout Barrier at the back waist to help prevent up to 100% of leaks, even blowouts. Featuring 50% more absorbent zones than ordinary diapers* to help distribute wetness evenly and keep baby’s skin dry and comfortable all night long. Less leaks mean more restful sleep. With Pampers Overnight Diapers, you can rest assured that you have superior absorbency, while keeping baby’s skin dry and healthy, no matter how baby sleeps. The BreatheFree Liner in Overnight Diapers size 3–7 wicks away moisture, allowing baby's skin to breathe, while the LockAway Channels pull wetness into the core of the diaper to help prevent irritation. Also, our best overnight diapers feature Dual Leak-Guard Barriers at the legs to help protect where leaks happen most. These nighttime diapers are dermatologist approved by the Skin Health Alliance, hypoallergenic, and free of parabens and latex,† so you can trust them to be safe and gentle on your little one’s delicate skin. Size 3–7 overnight diapers feature eight sweet nighttime prints. For trusted protection, trust Pampers, the #1 pediatrician recommended brand.** Product and packaging may vary. Download the Pampers Club App today and earn Pampers Cash*** Redeem your Pampers Cash for exclusive Pampers coupon savings and rewards. *Swaddlers Overnights vs. ”Everyday-of-the-year” brand **#1 Pediatrician Recommended Brand: Based on a 2021 survey of US & Canadian pediatricians. ***Only redeemable via Pampers Club. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best if your kiddo pees through og diapers
reviews.reviewText: My son always soaks through his original diaper overnight. Leaving him waking up an hour to two earlier with soaked PJs. But these diapers absorb more and we also pulled back on liquids before bed. They even have a good scent to them although I prefer unscented diapers.

reviews.reviewText: My daughter always wakes up dry when using these. They're comfortable, and hold a lot of urine. She can reliably sleep through the night with these on with no leaks or rash or anything. They don't have a scent, as far as I can tell.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Only diapers that don’t leak
reviews.reviewText: These are the only overnight diapers I could find for my son that he doesn’t pee through. He still has the occasional leak, but that’s usually when he drinks a lot of water right before bed. Prior to finding these I think we tried almost every other brand, and none of them kept his pajamas and sheets dry like these do.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Much better than Huggies for us
reviews.reviewText: Huggies did not work for our boy. We sized up to the largest size, and he would wake up most days soaked through his pajamas, sleep sack, and crib sheet. When we came to the end of the box, I decided to try a small box of these pampers overnights to see if they worked any better. He has waken up dry every single day. It’s actually astonishing, especially if you knew how much extra laundry I was doing before! Will definitely purchase again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My twin boys love these overnight diapers. Pampers Swaddlers is truly the best! They use 1 size bigger than their current day sizes, and that allows them to sleep longer and much more comfortable, along with plenty of barrier cream. Get these if you have a chance! You won’t regret it.
